OL,7,FThe UK economy has been crawling along
OL,8,Ffor the best part of 15 years and the
OL,9,Fresult is stagnating pay, over-
OL,10,Fstretched public services and a sharp
OL,11,Fincrease in the number of people who
OL,12,Fare struggling financially.
OL,14,FLow growth is not a uniquely British
OL,15,Fproblem, but new analysis by the
OL,16,FNational Institute of Economic and
OL,17,FSocial Research (NIESR) reveals that
OL,18,Fthe living standards of households in
OL,19,Fthe poorest parts of the UK are
OL,20,Flagging behind their counterparts in
OL,21,Fmany other countries.
